Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽昇起  然後落下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花朵盛開  然後凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽落下  然後昇起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花朵重新盛開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但和昨日相比又不同…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  還沒到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…既然是醫生介紹的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您應該也是醫生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是蟲師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣不信任我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你剛才聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那確實是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  這個職業我第一次聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  能看到島了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿古屋  你聽說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去到海的另一邊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一片廣闊而美麗的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家可以在那裡幸福地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候我帶你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.81,0:03:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  別再苦著個臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.89,0:03:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就該這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  為什麼只是遠遠的看著島
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上潮向就要改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是複雜的潮目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.58,jinggao,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}（潮目：暖流和寒流的分界線）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水流也很急
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入島就只有大潮的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉眼的工夫就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很簡單的就進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請小心頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是漁家的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個島裡沒有漁民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為每個月安全進出島的日子只有一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處都是岩石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這是個土地稀少的貧瘠島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在想辦法活著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有「活神仙」這個心靈支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「活神仙」？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有人  快藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  這個不能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是獻給「活神仙」的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須先治好你的病
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  忍一忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會好起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我們為什麼必須藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想見見那個「活神仙」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子只是個普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁邊是她的父親  這個島的島主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的身上每天都有奇蹟發生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是信徒參拜的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸完全停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個看到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看不見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吸了這些香氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的煩惱和病患都會一掃而空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不老不死之神的賜福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後還會恢復原來的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上醒來後就像什麼也沒發生一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然和你說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我也吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣病就能治好？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根本就是一派胡言！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我媽媽就是沒有治好而死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田裡的收成幾乎  全部獻給了「活神仙」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奉「活神仙」的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最早是由島主一族的人提起的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握潮水的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.21,0:07:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先進入島嶼的好像是島主的先祖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是從那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島主一族代代都會出現「活神仙」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到這消息的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看作是這島嶼的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也越來越多的遷居到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個「活神仙」死了後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.11,0:07:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出現新的「活神仙」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成這樣不過半年時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就有謠言說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸入「活神仙」發出的香氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不治之症也能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿古屋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又和外面的人一起玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來  有重要的事和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:08:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候前代「活神仙」剛剛過世一個月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天是起潮的日子  所以我記得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我聽到了他們的談話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「昨天的事情我不記得了」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「又有人死了」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過了一段時間後我終於明白了事情真相
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  又有治好的人出現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自我暗示起的效果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本就沒指望的阿古屋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也能起些作用就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能饒恕他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以決定出島尋找能治好阿古屋的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙他們說不再回來而出島了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是島主知道我回來了  一定會起疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話  銀古先生  你也很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了麻煩的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:08:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能這樣再讓大家被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘快讓我見一下本人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脈搏跳動得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體溫也比常人高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠟燭就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了  是蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,產子後成蟲死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.05,0:10:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病因是寄生在鼻腔裡的蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道拿掉後會不會好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,患者只有這個孩子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他幾個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被藏在島崖那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們大家也和阿古屋一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就有零星的這種病人出現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷代的島主發現有這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把他們藏在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為接近「活神仙」的狂熱信仰者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的家人都會為他們祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為自己家族出了脫離苦海的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果沒有新的發現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那個孩子發病的時候也是漲潮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漲水的時候才能去的地方有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島崖前面的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  這傢伙也被寄生了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該還有其它的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到附近到處找找
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又找到了兩隻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.82,0:11:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  先放在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈岐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治療的方法找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  阿古屋  安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿古屋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈岐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿古屋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.09,0:12:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？父親為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿古屋  離開小島吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有三天就是大潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:13:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間你先把病好了的消息瞞著島主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我喜歡這個小島
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親一定也不會放過我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會有其他人代替的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個原因治好了就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這個島上根治這種由蟲帶來的病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為「活神仙」時候的事  還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天我被父親叫去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿古屋  這是為你準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表像牽牛花  香味很濃的花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在懸崖的那個洞裡見過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:14:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面很暗  但確實有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天後嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  總之一定不要讓島主發現才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿古屋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前先扮演好「活神仙」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有以前的感覺了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得非常不安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為「活神仙」的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始衰弱著  睡著度過每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻總是覺得生活很充實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是閉著眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在卻感到很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:15:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使醒來也只是繼續昨天的現實而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對眼前虛無飄渺的時間洪流束手無策
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像是按照蟲的時間來生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種蟲會使宿主體內的時間和自己同步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生物的壽命根據種類不同而各異
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一生中脈搏跳動的次數據說是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同的只是體內時間流逝的密度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種蟲的壽命大約是一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你每天都經歷著這些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:53.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天  每一刻  對我都是新的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有煩惱  沒有憂愁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心裡  總是很充實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過半個時辰就能進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿古屋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時候你應該很衰弱才對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父…父親  我的病不知道為何已經好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈岐好像回來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像知道他去了哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  今天是大潮的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長在黑暗中的牽牛花  好濃的氣味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個部分就是蟲的巢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄生在生物上的蟲就是把卵產在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀古先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.03,0:17:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「活神仙」大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  請告訴我島崖的洞在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  「活神仙」大人會說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後會都告訴你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救奈岐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈岐  你在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋  居然還這麼悠閒…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別激動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管他  這種人不會有好下場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:18:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉迷於利用蟲而不能自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終究會自我毀滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用蟲的結果就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在挑釁  是不是有什麼想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.55,0:18:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來  奈岐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便把他們的屍體扔到海裡餵魚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他手裡拿著花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿古屋說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒人追來  但是好像漲潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  最多支撐半個時辰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人  找到了  是奈岐他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  讓開點  我們把縫隙砸開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親  父親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為你準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再苦著個臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿古屋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…呢  奈岐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能…活著到…那個世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比以前寄生的更嚴重了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要取出來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿古屋真正開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在身為「活神仙」的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽昇起  然後落下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花朵盛開  然後凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽落下  然後昇起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:21:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花朵重新盛開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖和昨日相比又不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但花朵今日依然美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時  逃過了漲潮的銀古先生在島上又待了一個月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此期間把島崖那裡得這種病的人都治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  在下次漲潮島崖下的洞穴再次打開的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定又有人會成為「活神仙」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.43,0:21:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕有人並不會感謝我的治療
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.39,0:21:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會再聞那些花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.28,0:21:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像阿古屋那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對眼前虛無飄渺的時間洪流  束手無策
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今往後  不知道該怎樣活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.59,0:22:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像普通人一樣活就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.47,0:22:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能捕到魚的話就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時間就乘船出海
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫大家一起把那個洞填了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是什麼容易的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.55,0:22:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  對於你來說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有很漫長的時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}「雨後彩虹」


